item.title: CVE-2021-38349|2024-09-17T03:59:39.305Z -- integration%20of%20moneybird%20for%20woocommerce -- integration%20of%20moneybird%20for%20woocommerce
item.description: The Integration of Moneybird for WooCommerce WordPress plugin is vulnerable to Reflected Cross-Site Scripting via the error_description parameter found in the ~/templates/wcmb-admin.php file which allows attackers to inject arbitrary web scripts, in versions up to and including 2.1.1.
